  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/650990/extras/973c0bf997028f0f7e6a6e6c8afdf348.avif?t=1497543528\" width=590 height=93 /></span><br><br>Run Jump Die Repeat is a single button platformer game. Press SPACE to run, bounce, jump, climb, and kill as you attempt to save the Cracker Princess and escape the evil Cron Rebels home planet.<br><br><strong>Featuring: </strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 50 increasingly challenging levels<br></li><li> 3 different game modes to play (story, classic, hardcore)<br></li><li> Simple yet engaging story mode<br></li><li> One button controls you'll have to learn to master<br></li><li> Death.. lots of deaths x_x</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/650990/extras/973c0bf997028f0f7e6a6e6c8afdf348.avif?t=1497543528\" width=590 height=93 /></span><br><br>Run Jump Die Repeat is a single button platformer game. Press SPACE to run, bounce, jump, climb, and kill as you attempt to save the Cracker Princess and escape the evil Cron Rebels home planet.<br><br><strong>Featuring: </strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 50 increasingly challenging levels<br></li><li> 3 different game modes to play (story, classic, hardcore)<br></li><li> Simple yet engaging story mode<br></li><li> One button controls you'll have to learn to master<br></li><li> Death.. lots of deaths x_x</li></ul>",
